f-drilling, and tapping screws. Additionally, the company provides design and material consultancy, project execution, site quality assurance, and dry construction methods training services. Furthermore, it engages in the sale of electricity generated from windmills. Ramco Industries Limited was incorporated in 1965 and is headquartered in Chennai, India."}}